sub_topic: The self-similarity of the Mandelbrot set.
message_1: What is the Hausdorff dimension of the boundary of the Mandelbrot set?
message_2: The Hausdorff dimension of the boundary of the Mandelbrot set is not known exactly. However, it is known to be greater than 1 and less than or equal to 2. The exact value is still an open question in mathematics.
